  "description": "Wrap yourself in the magic of Christmas with your colouring pens and cosiest blanket, as you explore the brand-new Cozy Christmas Colouring Book, a special collaboration between Coco Wyo and Penguin Random House. It’s the perfect gift for anyone looking to unwind and enjoy a little holiday cheer. With simple, cute pages you can complete in one sitting, picture yourself snuggled up, colouring relaxing scenes of snow-covered rooftops, cosy fireplaces, and festive joy. A perfect Christmas gift, or a gift to yourself to help you relax and escape – this beautiful book will delight colouring book lovers of all ages! • 45 hand-drawn pages ready for your creativity • Thick, high-quality paper • Large, bold designs that are easy to colour • Convenient 8 x 8-inch size, perfect for relaxing anywhere • Crisp, high-resolution illustrations that bring each page to life Read more",
